description:
&lt;p&gt;The Medical Education Department is seeking to appoint a Medical Education Administrativ&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Medical Education Department is seeking to appoint a Medical Education Administrative Assistant to support the delivery of medical education within our Clinical Education Centre.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking to recruit an enthusiastic and flexible team player who has excellent IT and communication skills to :&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;provide general administrative support for the Clinical Education Centre&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;support our Clinical Skills Team in the administration of clinical skills courses&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;work as a team member for Medical Education, to include both Postgraduate and Undergraduate Department&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this busy office environment you must be able to adapt to change, be able to work effectively under pressure and demonstrate an ability to prioritise and manage your own workload. You will also need to be flexible and able to work effectively as part of a wider team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This team is extremely busy so a ‘can do’ attitude and the ability to thrive under pressure are essential. You will be working with a diverse range of customers so confidence and a customer focused outlook is a must!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please ensure you read the person specification and align your application to this. Your application will be shortlisted by how well you meet the criteria stated within the person specification.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please note we reserve the right to close the post early if a sufficient number of applications are received. Please submit your application as soon as you are able.&lt;/p&gt;
